      <title>Markdown</title>
      <link href="2020/06/01/Markdown/"/>
      <url>2020/06/01/Markdown/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>工具：<a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/" title="🤔">vs code</a><br>插件:<code>Markdown</code> <code>Markdown pdf</code> <code>Markdown preview enhanced</code> <code>Markdown formatter</code> <code>Markdownlint</code><br><code>PS:</code>其实也可以只装个<code>Markdown All in One</code></p></blockquote><h3 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a><a id="01">标题</a></h3><p><code># 一级标题</code> <code>## 二级标题</code> <code>直到六级标题</code></p><h3 id="字体"><a href="#字体" class="headerlink" title="字体"></a>字体</h3><p><em>斜体</em>  <code>*斜体*</code>  <strong>粗体</strong>  <code>**粗体**</code>  <strong><em>粗斜体</em></strong>  <code>***粗斜体***</code>  <del>删除线</del>  <code>~~删除线~~</code></p><a id="more"></a><h3 id="段落引用"><a href="#段落引用" class="headerlink" title="段落引用"></a>段落引用</h3><blockquote><p>&gt; + 文字(一级)</p><blockquote><p>&gt;&gt; + 文字(二级)</p><blockquote><p>&gt;&gt;&gt; + 文字(三级)</p></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><h3 id="分割线"><a href="#分割线" class="headerlink" title="分割线"></a>分割线</h3><ul><li>使用三个或以上的 *和_都可</li></ul><hr><h3 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a>图片</h3><ul><li><p>行内式语法</p></li><li><p>![图片名称](图片地址 “图片提示”)</p></li><li><p>图片名称就是对图片内容的解释，如果图片因为某些原因不能显示，  就用定义的图片名称文字来代替图片。图片提示是当鼠标悬停在图片上时显示的提示内容。图片提示可加可不加</p></li><li><p>链接本地图片:![](地址\filename.etc)</p></li></ul><h3 id="超链接"><a href="#超链接" class="headerlink" title="超链接"></a>超链接</h3><h4 id="行内式"><a href="#行内式" class="headerlink" title="行内式"></a>行内式</h4><ul><li>[超链接名称](超链接地址 “超链接提示”)</li><li>例 : <a href="http://www.github.com/" title="🥰">GitHub</a></li></ul><h4 id="自动链接"><a href="#自动链接" class="headerlink" title="自动链接"></a>自动链接</h4><ul><li>&lt;链接&gt;如 <a href="https://zhuqin.top/">https://zhuqin.top</a></li></ul><h4 id="参考式"><a href="#参考式" class="headerlink" title="参考式"></a>参考式</h4><ul><li><p>[名称][代号]</p></li><li><p>[代号]:地址</p></li></ul><h3 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h3><ol><li>无序列表用 - + *任何一种开头都可以。注意- + *跟内容之间要有一个空格  </li><li>有序列表用数字加点为开头。注意序号跟内容之间要有一个空格</li><li>列表嵌套在VS Code里用Tab键就能使用列表嵌套的功能，上一级与下一级的序号之间相差2个空格(也有配置成3个空格的)</li></ol><blockquote><p>例</p></blockquote><ul><li>列表1<ul><li>二级列表1<ul><li>三级列表1</li></ul></li></ul></li><li>列表2<ul><li>二级列表2<ul><li>三级列表2</li></ul></li></ul></li><li>列表3</li></ul><ol><li>列表1<ol><li>二级列表1<ol><li>三级列表1</li></ol></li></ol></li><li>列表2</li></ol><h3 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h3><ul><li>每一行用|分割列。第二行分割表头和内容，可以在这里控制该列的对齐方式。左边有 ‘:’ 表示左对齐，右边有 ‘:’ 表示右对齐，两边都有 ‘:’ 表示居中对齐，中间的 ‘-‘ 是为了占满空间</li></ul><blockquote><p>例</p></blockquote><table><thead><tr><th align="left">左对齐</th><th align="right">右对齐</th><th align="center">居中对齐</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">1</td><td align="right">2</td><td align="center">3</td></tr><tr><td align="left">a</td><td align="right">b</td><td align="center">c</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h3><ol><li>单行代码 : 代码之间分别用一个反引号( ` )括起来<ul><li><code>#include&lt;iostream&gt;</code></li></ul></li><li>代码块 : 代码前后各一行用三个反引号( ``` )括起来第一个```后写上代码类型</li></ol><pre class="language-c" data-language="c"><code class="language-c"><span class="token macro property"><span class="token directive-hash">#</span><span class="token directive keyword">include</span><span class="token string">&lt;iostream></span></span><span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>    std<span class="token operator">::</span>cout<span class="token operator">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="token string">"hello markdown"</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span></code></pre><h3 id="脚注"><a href="#脚注" class="headerlink" title="脚注"></a>脚注</h3><ul><li>待解释[^name]<br>然后[^name]:内容</li></ul><blockquote><p>列 :待解释<a href="%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8A">^1</a></p><blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><h3 id="任务列表"><a href="#任务列表" class="headerlink" title="任务列表"></a>任务列表</h3><pre class="language-c" data-language="c"><code class="language-c"><span class="token operator">*</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span>x<span class="token punctuation">]</span> 内容<span class="token operator">*</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> 内容   x表示已完成</code></pre><h3 id="锚点"><a href="#锚点" class="headerlink" title="锚点"></a>锚点</h3><ul><li>例: 跳转到<a href="#01">标题</a></li></ul><pre class="language-html" data-language="html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class="token attr-name">id</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>01<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>1.标题<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span> 跳转到[1.标题](#01)</code></pre><h3 id="Todo列表"><a href="#Todo列表" class="headerlink" title="Todo列表"></a>Todo列表</h3><ul><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 123</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 456</li></ul><pre class="language-markdown" data-language="markdown"><code class="language-markdown">使用带有 [ ] 或 [x] （未完成或已完成）项的列表语法撰写一个待办事宜列表，并且支持子列表嵌套以及混用Markdown语法<span class="token list punctuation">*</span> [ ] 123<span class="token list punctuation">*</span> [x] 456</code></pre><h3 id="注意"><a href="#注意" class="headerlink" title="注意"></a><strong>注意</strong></h3><ul><li>换行需要<strong>两个空格加回车</strong></li><li>&amp;emsp;表示缩进一个中文字符</li><li>&amp;ensp;表示缩进半个中文字符</li><li>&amp;nbsp;表示缩进1/4个中文字符</li><li>全文使用的无序列表的序号应当一致</li><li>代码区```后写明语言</li><li>全文统一无序列表符</li><li>\表示转义字符防止[（等打印不出）</li></ul><h3 id="html拓展"><a href="#html拓展" class="headerlink" title="html拓展"></a>html拓展</h3><p><code>文字居中</code></p><div align=center>hello world</div><center>Hello World</center><pre class="language-html" data-language="html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class="token attr-name">align</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span>center</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>hello world<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>OR<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>center</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>Hello World<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>center</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre><p><code>折叠</code></p><details open><summary>折叠</summary><ul><li><input checked disabled="" type="checkbox">甲</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox">乙</li></ul></details><pre class="language-html" data-language="html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>details</span> <span class="token attr-name">open</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>summary</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>折叠<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>summary</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>ul</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>li</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class="token attr-name">checked</span> <span class="token attr-name">disabled</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">type</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>checkbox<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>甲<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>li</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class="token attr-name">disabled</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">type</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>checkbox<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>乙<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>details</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre><p><code>图片</code></p><p>并排</p><pre class="language-html" data-language="html"><code class="language-html">|url|url||:-:|:-:|</code></pre><p>大小<br><code>&lt;img src=&quot;http:...&quot; width = &quot;100&quot; height = &quot;100&quot; div align=right /&gt;</code><br>可 width = “100” height = “100”设置图片大小。<br>也可： width = 20% height = 20%</p><p><code>插入空行</code></p><br><p><code>&lt;br&gt;</code></p><p><code>注释</code></p><!--你看不见!--><p><code>&lt;!--你看见了--&gt;</code><br><code>F12</code>看源码找注释</p><h3 id="附"><a href="#附" class="headerlink" title="附"></a>附</h3><ul><li>各种图：<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/69495726">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/69495726</a></li><li>公式：<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/25f0139637b7">https://www.jianshu.com/p/25f0139637b7</a></li></ul><p><strong>未完待续</strong></p>]]></content>
      
      
